{"word":"G5215 - ὕμνος - hýmnos - hoom'-nos - Hymn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὕμνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hýmnos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoom'-nos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hymn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஞானப்பாட்டு - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a song in praise of gods, heroes, conquerors"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Apparently from a simpler (obsolete) form of <b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>hudeo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>celebrate</i>; probably akin to <a href=\"#/G103 - ᾄδω - áidō - ad'-o/103\">G103</a>; compare <a href=\"#/G5567 - ψάλλω - psállō - psal'-lo/5567\">G5567</a>); a &ldquo;hymn&rdquo; or religious ode (one of the Psalms): - hymn."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5214 - ὑμνέω - hymnéō - hoom-neh'-o/5214\">G5214</a>, <a href=\"#/G5215 - ὕμνος - hýmnos - hoom'-nos/5215\">G5215</a>"}]}